To create an interactive pie chart that displays the market share of different movie genres in a selected year, we need to focus on the 'Major Genre' and 'Release Date' attributes from the dataset. This chart will allow users to select different years and compare the distribution of genres within those years. Here's the Vega-Lite JSON specification for the interactive pie chart:

```json
{
  "$schema": "https://vega.github.io/schema/vega-lite/v5.json",
  "description": "An interactive pie chart showing the market share of different genres in a selected year.",
  "data": {
    "url": "data/movies.json",
