To create an area chart illustrating cumulative box office earnings over time segmented by genre, we can use the following Vega-Lite JSON specification. This visualization will provide insights into how different genres have contributed to box office earnings over time, revealing trends and patterns in the film industry.

```json
{
  "$schema": "https://vega.github.io/schema/vega-lite/v5.json",
