To conclude the financial narrative, we will create a heat map that illustrates profitability by budget range and genre. This visualization will help us understand how different budget levels and genres correlate with profitability, offering a comprehensive view of the film industry's financial landscape.

```json
{
  "$schema": "https://vega.github.io/schema/vega-lite/v5.json",
